body:

The 2018 edition of PyConDE & PyData Karlsruhe took place 24–26 October 2018 at the ZKM in Karlsruhe. Browse the [archived talks](talks/) and [speakers](speakers/) below, or revisit the [original conference site](https://2018.de.pycon.org/).
